title: 12 video Mixtapes rare and not online!
description:
I recently tried to acquire a bunch of out of date and rare mix tapes from a snail mail trade on Cinemageddon.

I bring you a torrent with all 12 I have acquired!
They are:

Amok Assult Video (1 hour)
Asylum for Shut ins Video Pdychotherapy (40 minutes)
B-Videos 101 Vol 1 (2 hours)
Evil Video 1 (2 hours)
Future Schlock Vol 1 (1 hour)
Gravedigger Eye Pollution (2 hours)
Immondo Videozine 1 (2 hours)
Lost Purity (1 hr 30 min)
Mental Vagrancy (2 hours)
Super Mecha Kucha Happy Fun Monkey Bash Dx (1 hr 30 min)
The Ultimate Hardgore Splatter Tape (1 hour)
Video Wasteland Combilation (2 hours)

All in standard xvid re-encoded from DVD sources you can now buy here! <a href="
http://www.ioffer.com/items/inventory_list/drdemento456" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.ioffer.com/items/inventory_list/drdemento456</a>

But in all seriousness I can see why a vast majority of these tapes were lost for some time (Some recorded back in 1993 and on was even recorded from VHS back in 2004!)

Truthfully I can see maybe 4-5 of these tapes were half way decent, and some blew my mind! (In Evil video these Vietnamese people eat a freakin puppy! In front of their children!)

Anyway some of the tapes I highly recommend are B-Videos 101, Evil Video, Lost Purity, The Ultimate Hardgore Splatter Tape, and Super Mecha Kucha Happy Fun Monkey Bash Dx (if your really into the Japanese thing), Mental Vagrancy, and Video Wasteland.

Enjoy guys!
